This file serves as a short-term roadmap for the project.
It will be updated regularly as new features are planned and implemented.


Upcoming Features
=================
+ Add collision detection for worm body
+ Add apples to grow worm
+ Track and display points
+ Add basic obstacles
+ Add a second worm that moves randomly
+ Give second worm basic intelligence to avoid obstacles
+ Animate apples
+ Enable apples to move around autonomously


Implemented
===========
